name: Moirai’s hands
description: The inexorable Moirai spin the threads of destinies.  Everything that happens is the work of their spindle, and all events happen exactly as they have woven from the beginning.  What is it?  Destiny, fate that everyone receives at birth? Do we choose because we want to or because the Moirai have decided for us? Every action, every word, every turn of life. We rejoice and become upset, we succeed and we fall under the weight of mistakes. We think we can change and can be changed.  And in the meantime, Moirai continue to spin...
